ne of the previous stable version:\n+\n+  ```markdown\n+  Current stable, released 20YY-MM-DD -> Released 20YY-MM-DD\n+  ```\n+\n [how to update the changelog]: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust-clippy/blob/master/doc/changelog_update.md"}]}